    <p class="auto-style2">1. How to report an item? </p> 
     
    <p class="auto-style2">  Once you login, select sub-categories under categories, and click view details. Then, you are re-directed to the page with options to report the seller</p>
    <p class="auto-style2">2. How to edit profile?</p>
    <p class="auto-style2">   Under my profile, you can update your profile, view it and also, change your password.</p>
    <p class="auto-style2">3. How to delete my account?</p>
    <p class="auto-style2">   Visit the about us page for admin details. A simple email request to any of the admins will help you remove your account .</p>
    <p class="auto-style2">4. How to place an ad?</p>
    <p class="auto-style2">   After logging in, beside my profile you can find place my ad option</p>
    <p class="auto-style2">For further assistance, please visit about us page and email any of the admins.</p>
    <p class="auto-style2">5. Steps to place an ad?</p>
    <p class="auto-style2">   Select a category from the dropdown, and give a nice title to your Ad.
              Quote a price to your item in $, and provide your contact details so that buyer can contact you using them.
        Click Place Ad, That's it! You're done with posting. Wait to meet a buyer soon!
    </p>
